list.name: Default
list.comment: Added the Swing GUI with the text-based interation pane. Refactored the editor system to eliminate singletons. Added a first attempt to a sphere generator (doesn't work yet)

changelist.name: Default
changelist.comment: Removed "The old man the boat" test case. Cleaned up SceneModel, renamed it. Renamed SceneStatement to SceneCommand, cleaned up and refactored to adhere to command pattern.

task.summary: Translated to Java. (Yep, you read that right)
Fixed some of te testcases. Added extra tests, fixed ParseTree toString()
Fixed some tests. Split EntityCreateRule into its' own file. Added Serializeable to Knowledge
Re-organised the project into modules, cleaned up the git repo.
Removed "old" files. (Should not have been comitted in the first place) Started work on the "ConcreteModelling" module.
Added the Renderer/Visualizer module. Refactorings and small changes.
Got the system to the point where it draws arbitrary meshes.
Added the concept of a GroupModel. Simplified the CompositeModel, removed ModelInstances.
Added the Swing GUI with the text-based interation pane. Refactored the editor system to eliminate singletons. Added a first attempt to a sphere generator (doesn't work yet)
